    "description": "<h2>Welcome to Sentron Engineering (S) Pte Ltd</h2>\n<p>*<strong>Sentron Engineering(S) Pte Ltd</strong> is established in 1993,<br>\n*We obtained <strong>Registry of BCA Contractor</strong>, <strong>bizSAFE Level 5</strong>, <strong>Registry of ISO Quality Management and OHSAS</strong>.<br>\n*We specialize in <strong>Residential</strong>, <strong>Commercial buildings</strong> and <strong>Industrial Building ACMV Installation</strong>,<br>\n*We are equipped with a team of <strong>Devoted</strong>, <strong>Skilled</strong> and <strong>Professional Technicians</strong> to support our clients,<br>\n*We are committed to <strong>High Quality Services</strong> and <strong>Skill Standards</strong>,<br>\n*We have practical <strong>Experiences</strong> and <strong>Capabilities</strong> to handle and oversee project from conceptual design, fabrication to final delivery stage.</p>",
